node.text:
I couldn’t fit all of the love in this video but this just shows how many AMAZING members of the education community we have. This video is dedicated to every single one of YOU. We love you, we appreciate you and are incredibly proud of everything you are doing.

THANK YOU!!! 🤍🤍🤍

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'i walk around like everything is ok... but deep down inside, i want to put up my Christmas tree.'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on September 05, 2021. May be a meme of text that says 'Me when someone who doesn't work in education says they don't understand how teachers haven't completely lost their shit yet this year: @teachertrauma WE RE CLOSE'.

Photo by Teacher Tips and Fun! 👨‍🏫🧑‍🏫 on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'To My Teacher Bestie, thanks for WATCHING MY CLASS WHILE USE THE RESTROOM SAVING ME PIECE OF CAKE FROM THE BREAK ROOM. SHARING YOUR STUDENT HORROR STORIES TO REMIND ME AM NOT ALONE. LISTENING TO CRY WITHOUT JUDGING. SENDING ME TEXT TO MAKE ME LAUGH WHEN I'M HAVING ROUGH DAY. LINK IN CAPTION'.
